Dictionary.description: -- Definition -- Types of access restrictions for a transport element.

Definition.description: -- Definition -- Access to the transport element is forbidden by law.
Definition.name: forbiddenLegally

Definition.description: -- Definition -- Access to the transport element is physically impossible due to the presence of barriers or other physical obstacles.
Definition.name: physicallyImpossible

Definition.description: -- Definition -- Access to the transport element is restricted because it is privately owned.
Definition.name: private

Definition.description: -- Definition -- The transport element is open to public access.
Definition.name: publicAccess

Definition.description: -- Definition -- Access to the transport element depends on the season.
Definition.name: seasonal

Definition.description: -- Definition -- Access to the transport element is subject to toll.
Definition.name: toll
